xt"},{"text":"spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":") and sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider/spacePaddingBlock":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider\/spacePaddingBlock","type":"topic","title":"spacePaddingBlock","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider\/spacepaddingblock","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spacePaddingBlock","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SpaceSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token spaces.paddingBlockMedium","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider/spaceRowGapBullet":{"title":"spaceRowGapBullet","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider\/spacerowgapbullet","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spaceRowGapBullet","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SpaceSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token spaces.rowGapNone","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider\/spaceRowGapBullet","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"Theme Orange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"